{"build_type":"library","description":"The single place that writes the LLM-reader response envelope's shared tail and emits it, so that format lives in ONE location (the plan's 'cement'). Given an env object already carrying its op-specific payload fields and its inline confidence, attach the shared tail in a fixed order — omitted, then hash — skipping any argument passed as 0 (ops that lack one omit it cleanly), then write env to stdout. omitted is a mapping document value (or 0); hash is a string handle (or 0). Confidence stays inline in each op (it is branch-dependent), always under the key 'confidence'. Reuses add_str_field, attach_named_member_inside_mapping, emit_result_object_onto_standard_output.","module_name":"complete-reading-response-envelope-document","package_name":"complete-reading-response-envelope-document","function_definitions":{"complete-reading-response-envelope-document":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"env","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"omitted","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"hash","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_omitted","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"omitted"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_hash","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"hash"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"omitted"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"attach-named-member-inside-mapping","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"env"},{"kind":"var","value":"s_omitted"},{"kind":"var","value":"omitted"}]}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"hash"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"attach-string-member-towards-mapping","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"env"},{"kind":"var","value":"s_hash"},{"kind":"var","value":"hash"}]}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"write-result-object-toward-standard-output","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"env"}],"result_assignment_variable":"w","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}]}}}